To make the logging libraries, use make as normal (its makefile is Makefile).

To make the process info libraries, use make -f Makefile.procinfo (its
makefile is Makefile.procinfo).

Something I would have like to know when I had to use this:
The RULES environment variable has to be set to the directory containing the rules you want to use (e.g. unix if you're on solaris, etc...).